title: Survival Quest ( DVD, 2007) Leading Role: Lance Henriksen
description:
Movie Description
While learning how to survive alone in the wilderness, a group of students encounters another survival school run by a mercenary with questionable methods. With their instructor murdered, the group must use their new skills to return to safety before being killed.

Credits 
Cast: Lance Henriksen 
Director: Don Coscarelli 

Industry Reviews
"...Full of bright movie images....SURVIVAL QUEST is sheer movie athleticism..."
Los Angeles Times - Michael Wilmington (03/27/1990)
